## Interface: 20505
## Title: Super Swing Timer
## Notes: Melee, ranged, and current-target enemy swing timer for Classic and TBC. Includes Blizzard options panel support, a top Quick Controls section with toggle and color columns, slimmer 15px main bars with a derived 10px OH bar, class-colored swing bars with opacity-aware color swatches, a Rogue latency-adjusted Sinister Strike end-window cue on the MH bar, a test Rogue vertical energy-tick helper, a red-by-default enemy bar with an in-game toggle and color control, spark positioning synced to the actual status-bar fill with a 3px default width, in-addon texture previews, a hunter Auto Shot cooldown line with configurable safe/unsafe window colors, a dedicated Hunter Auto Shot / Multi-Shot cast bar, adjustable bar border size, dedicated spark and weave texture browsers, bar-only texture filtering, a UnitAura-aware paladin seal breakpoint line, a temporary Test Bars preview for moving frames, and color-coded shaman weave assist overlays with per-family toggles that stay above the bar fill.
